016package org.lifstools.jmzqc;
017
018import java.util.Objects;
019
020/**
021 * Base element for a term that is defined in a controlled vocabulary, with
022 * OPTIONAL value.
023 *
024 * Type of input file.
025 */
026public class CvParameter {
027
028    private String accession;
029    private String description;
030    private String name;
031    private Object value;
032
033    public CvParameter(){}
034    
035    public CvParameter(String accession, String description, String name, Object value) {
036        this.accession = accession;
037        this.description = description;
038        this.name = name;
039        this.value = value;
040    }
041
042    public String getAccession() {
043        return accession;
044    }
045
046    public void setAccession(String accession) {
047        this.accession = accession;
048    }
049
050    public String getDescription() {
051        return description;
052    }
053
054    public void setDescription(String description) {
055        this.description = description;
056    }
057
058    public String getName() {
059        return name;
060    }
061
062    public void setName(String name) {
063        this.name = name;
064    }
065
066    public Object getValue() {
067        return value;
068    }
069
070    public void setValue(Object value) {
071        this.value = value;
072    }
073
074    @Override
075    public int hashCode() {
076        int hash = 7;
077        hash = 19 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.accession);
078        hash = 19 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.description);
079        hash = 19 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.name);
080        hash = 19 * hash + Objects.hashCode(this.value);
081        return hash;
082    }
083
084    @Override
085    public boolean equals(Object obj) {
086        if (this == obj) {
087            return true;
088        }
089        if (obj == null) {
090            return false;
091        }
092        if (getClass() != obj.getClass()) {
093            return false;
094        }
095        final CvParameter other = (CvParameter) obj;
096        if (!Objects.equals(this.accession, other.accession)) {
097            return false;
098        }
099        if (!Objects.equals(this.description, other.description)) {
100            return false;
101        }
102        if (!Objects.equals(this.name, other.name)) {
103            return false;
104        }
105        return Objects.equals(this.value, other.value);
106    }
107
108}
